            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#TA">
                <p>To the Shades of the Underworld. Cornelia Soteris lived 85 years. Auctus, her brother, made this.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>ISic000161-000164 were all found together and, as Bivona notes, should all belong to the same family, since they share the same nomen (Cornelius) and the Auctus of <ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000161">ISic000161</ref> is the dedicant for his wife (<ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000163">ISic000163</ref>) and, in this text, his sister. The relationship of Cornelius Castor in <ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000162">ISic000162</ref> to the other three is not known (could be a son or grandson given the ages).</p>
            </div>
